item.title: Cheerful Loving Couple Bakers Drinking Coffee
item.description: I just told you! You’ve killed me! Do a flip! I didn’t ask for a completely reasonable excuse! I asked you to get busy! It’s okay, Bender. I like cooking too. Calculon is gonna kill us and it’s all everybody else’s fault! Oh, I don’t have time for this. I have to go and buy a single piece of fruit with a coupon and then return it, making people wait behind me while I complain.
